</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/42293519-ragtimes2-garnes">Ragtimes2 Garnes</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is my favorite book. I did a summer book club and this was one of the books we read and discussed. I found the beginning of the book heart breaki<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is my favorite book. I did a summer book club and this was one of the books we read and discussed. I found the beginning of the book heart breaking but I was captivated and could not put it down until I completed the entire book. I passed it on to my daughters because I wished for them the same healing, the main character experienced. Four of my daughter, I rescued from abuse. In the same manner the oldest child was not accepting of me as was the main character of the one who loved her. Reading this book also thought me lessons about love. I learned that it is not until we are mature enough and ready to receive love that we can accept and return love. We live and learn.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
