<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/765112-will-there-be-a-movie-based-on-the-book">Will there be a movie based on the book?!!!!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_765112'><a id="like_count_community_question_765112" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/765112?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11422.Redeeming_Love">like</a></span>

